quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  97,1,Yaqeenan hum nay issay shab qadar mein nazil farmaya
  97,2,To kiaya janey kay shab qadar kiya hy
  97,3,Shab qadar aik hazar maheeno say behter hai
  97,4,Iss (mein her kaam) kay siranjam denay ko apney rab kay hukum say farishty aur rooh(jibrael)utertay hain
  97,5,Yeh raat sir-a-sir slamti ki hoti hai aur fajar kay tuloo honay tak(rehti hai)